MakeMyTrip.com/Yatra/Booking.com

Functional Requirements:
1.User should be able to search flights based on arrival + destination+ date of travel
2.User should be able to login to application.
3.Select the flight based on time/preference.
4.Enter the personal details.
5.Make payment in your application.
6.Notification to the email.

Non-Functional Requirements
1.Scalable
2.Reliable
3.Modular

Finding the actors
1.User
2.Airline authority
3.Admin

Entities:
1.User
2.Flights
3.Booking
4.Payment
5.Notification
6.Airline



